Witha  57 war &amp; a 52 paladin I think I can safely say that the best tank for xp groups is a paladin.  SKs are close but chain stunning is just about the best taunt I've ever seen.  The damage won't be quite as high as a warrior but it'll be 75% or so and with a monk or rouge rarely/never having to pull thier punches we actually end up causing MORE damage to the mob than a warrior...it's just indirect.<br>
